query:
INSERT INTO scheduled_executions (id, task_id, project_id, scheduled_at, executor_profile_id, repos)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
               RETURNING
                   id                  AS "id!: Uuid",
                   task_id             AS "task_id!: Uuid",
                   project_id          AS "project_id!: Uuid",
                   scheduled_at        AS "scheduled_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                   status              AS "status!: ScheduledExecutionStatus",
                   executor_profile_id,
                   repos,
                   created_at          AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                   updated_at          AS "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                   fired_at            AS "fired_at: DateTime<Utc>",
                   error_message
